text: Georgina von Wilczek (24 October 1921 – 18 October 1989) was the Princess of Liechtenstein as the wife of Prince Regnant Franz Joseph II. She is the mother of Hans-Adam II and his four siblings. Princess Georgina died in Grabs, Switzerland after an unknown illness. == Titles == * 24 October 1921 – 7 March 1943: Countess Georgina von Wilczek * 7 March 1943 – 18 October 1989: Her Serene Highness The Princess of Liechtenstein Category:1921 births Category:1989 deaths
